  <h2 class="section-title">Can Recall Data Provide Market Insight for a Strong Investment Strategy?</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">Every vehicle recall leaves a trail of breadcrumbs weeks before the public announcement — in consumer complaints, government investigations, and technical service bulletins. The market ignores these signals. We built a system to capture them.</p>

  <div class="phases">
