      <p>Complaint spikes appear in the NHTSA database. TSBs accelerate. Investigations open. The market ignores all of it. Our XGBoost model fires a STRONG SIGNAL 30–90 days before the recall is public. Riverdale enters the short position here.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="phase phase-2">
      <div class="phase-num">02</div>
