      <ul>
        <li><strong>Recall announced:</strong> Exit at market close the day after filing. Captured the entire gradual drift downward that happened weeks before the market reacted.</li>
        <li><strong>Stock rises 5%+:</strong> Stop loss exits the position automatically. Protects Riverdale from runaway losses.</li>
        <li><strong>Neither happens:</strong> Position closes after 45 days — the survival analysis median time from signal to recall filing.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
